Package dooyit.storage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CategoryController
    The CategoryController is a facade class for the StorageController to save or load categories
    CategoryDataDeserializer
    The CategoryDataDeserializer converts the JSON representation of CategoryData to a CategoryData object.
    CategoryLoader
    The CategoryLoader class contains methods and attributes necessary for loading categories.
    CategorySaver
    The CategorySaver class contains methods and attributes necessary for saving categories.
    Constants
    The Constants class holds all the Storage constants which are shared by the various classes in the Storage component
    DateTimeDeserializer
    The DateTimeDeserializer converts the JSON representation of DateTime to a DateTime object
    DateTimeSerializer
    The DateTimeSerializer converts the DateTime object to a JSON object
    Loader<T>  
    Saver<T>  
    StorageController
    The StorageController class provides methods and attributes necessary for loading and saving categories, tasks and custom css.
    TaskController
    The TaskController is a facade class for the StorageController to save or load tasks
    TaskDataDeserializer
    The TaskDataDeserializer creates the TaskData object from its JSON representation for loading
    TaskLoader
    The TaskLoader class contains methods and attributes necessary for loading tasks.
    TaskSaver
    The TaskSaver class contains methods and attributes necessary for saving tasks.
